data.description: Like New!! This home is only 3.5 years young! It's not your typical new construction! The first of the 3 porches greet you when you walk-in to the living room.There is also a  separate dinning room with French doors that lead out to one of the 2nd porch! The kitchen is open with beautiful cabinets, quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The primary bedroom and bath is like your private oasis! The primary bedroom is nice sized with a sliding glass door to the the deck and oversized backyard. It also has a large closet and recessed lights. The primary bath has a stand alone shower with multi head shower and a beautiful soaking tub. Hall access to the large backyard. Extra deep lot!
